<p><img class='alignnone' alt='' src='./ff4_images/ff4_part_3-1/01-sub-event-010.png' width='486' height='326' /><br /> <span style='color: #ffffff;'>-</span><br /> <span style='color: #ffffff;'> -</span><br /> 先在祕銀村把氣墊船放下，然後換乘氣墊船往東南方前進</p>
